# Trivy ignore file.
#
# Referenced by .github/workflows/security.yml (trivyignores: ".trivyignore").
# List vulnerability IDs (one per line, optionally with an expiry date) to
# suppress known/accepted findings, e.g.:
#
#   CVE-2024-12345 exp:2026-12-31
#
# Keep empty when there is nothing to suppress; the scanner requires the file to
# exist.
